OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773176765
OL,3,CPupils return to in-person lessons
OL,4,Cafter SEND school destroyed by fire
OL,6,FAll pupils at a school for SEND
OL,7,Fchildren destroyed by a fire in
OL,8,FOkehampton are expected to return to
OL,9,Fclassroom-based learning by the end of
OL,10,Fnext week.
OL,12,FContractors are working at three sites
OL,13,Faround the town to provide new
OL,14,Ftemporary classrooms for The Promise
OL,15,FSchool pupils who have been working at
OL,16,Fhome for more than a fortnight.
OL,18,FA disused wing of Okehampton Primary
OL,19,FSchool is one of the locations being
OL,20,Fused for the children's return.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
