FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773176765
OL,3,CPupils return to in-person lessons
OL,4,Cafter SEND school destroyed by fire
OL,6,FHeadteacher Quentin Gunderson said:
OL,7,F"We have to make the spaces safe, but
OL,8,Fwe also have to make them feel homely
OL,9,Fand welcoming."
OL,11,FHe added: "We are phasing their return
OL,12,Fback, just so it's not so overwhelming
OL,13,Fand we're getting used to working in
OL,14,Fthis space."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773176765
OL,3,CPupils return to in-person lessons
OL,4,Cafter SEND school destroyed by fire
OL,6,FOn Monday 9 March, Mr Gunderson
OL,7,Fexplained: "We've had our year elevens
OL,8,Fback all last week - they've been back
OL,9,Fin again doing their mock exams today.
OL,10,FOur primary will start returning from
OL,11,Ftomorrow, and then the rest of school
OL,12,Fwill be from sometime next week."
OL,14,FHe noted: "Our parents have been so
OL,15,Funderstanding and patient. It's not
OL,16,Feasy when your child doesn't have
OL,17,Ftheir school."
OL,19,FThe mother of one pupil explained it
OL,20,Fhas been a "struggle" to entertain her
OL,21,Fson over the last two weeks.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773176765
OL,3,CPupils return to in-person lessons
OL,4,Cafter SEND school destroyed by fire
OL,6,FKat Carthew says the situation has
OL,7,Fbeen hard to manage with her 10-year-
OL,8,Fold son Tommy, alongside running her
OL,9,Fphotography business in Tiverton,
OL,11,FShe said: "Trying to navigate life
OL,12,Fwith a SEND child, a business, five
OL,13,Fother children, trying to do
OL,14,Feverything...
OL,16,F"It's alright so far, but it's trying
OL,17,Fto keep him entertained - because he's
OL,18,Fon-the-go all the time."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773176765
OL,3,CPupils return to in-person lessons
OL,4,Cafter SEND school destroyed by fire
OL,6,FMs Carthew explained: "He's completely
OL,7,Fout of routine and he has had some
OL,8,Fmoments of dysregulation."
OL,10,FShe added: "With a SEND child, they
OL,11,Fare like ten children in one."
OL,13,FAccording to her, the school's
OL,14,Fresponse has been "phenomenal" and
OL,15,FTommy has received a laptop and
OL,16,Fworkbooks, but he is still struggling
OL,17,Fwithout his usual routine.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773176765
OL,3,CPupils return to in-person lessons
OL,4,Cafter SEND school destroyed by fire
OL,6,FAlthough he is due to have some in-
OL,7,Fperson lessons on Wednesday and
OL,8,FFriday, Ms Carthew is concerned Tommy
OL,9,Fwon't want to attend these classes in
OL,10,Fa new location.
OL,12,F"Hopefully it goes smoothly, but with
OL,13,Fa SEND child, you can't guarantee,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,FTeacher Christen Janes, known as CJ by
OL,17,Fthe children, is looking forward to
OL,18,Fwelcoming her pupils back.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773176765
OL,3,CPupils return to in-person lessons
OL,4,Cafter SEND school destroyed by fire
OL,6,FShe said the school has had "lots of
OL,7,Fsupport" in the form of donations and
OL,8,Fother help.
OL,10,FShe explained: "While we were waiting
OL,11,Fand doing online learning, we were
OL,12,Fprinting and getting everything
OL,13,Flaminated and ready to go for when we
OL,14,Fcould get in a space.
OL,16,F"Everything in here is exactly as it
OL,17,Fwas in my original room, I printed all
OL,18,Fthe same materials for them."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773176765
OL,3,CPupils return to in-person lessons
OL,4,Cafter SEND school destroyed by fire
OL,6,FShe added: "Everything is the same -
OL,7,Fto their name plates on the desk,
OL,8,Ftheir social and emotional check-ins,
OL,9,Ftheir schedules..."
OL,11,FMs Janes noted that this "consistency
OL,12,Fand routine" is key for the SEND
OL,13,Fpupils.J"That is so important to them,
OL,14,Fit's how they thrive," she said.
OL,16,FThe Promise School blaze started on
OL,17,FSunday 22 February and firefighters
OL,18,Ftackled it overnight.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
