OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773176765
OL,3,CPupils return to in-person lessons
OL,4,Cafter SEND school destroyed by fire
OL,6,FDevon and Somerset Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService said 18 crews attended at the
OL,8,Fheight of the fire, with six fire
OL,9,Fappliances, two aerial ladder
OL,10,Fplatforms and two water carriers used.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
